{"tid":2189002,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"全民檢測︱楊明被盜用身份證登記　姚瑩瑩曹永廉同樣中招","createTime":"2020-09-04T14:51:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T16:44:06.000Z","uid":16659,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a0957b1d868b78a1c5f9e90f3ed1613d75363c59","tid":2189002,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T14:51:39.000Z","msg":"楊明與女友莊思明今日（4/9）接受全民檢測「普及社區檢測計劃」，更在Instagram貼出一張在採樣中心門前拍攝的合照。雖然楊明在帖文中指出檢測過程順暢，但原來發生了一段小插曲，因為身份證資料曾被人盜用作登記檢測，甚至有人冒認有關部門致電給他：「好彩，工作人員好好，都畀我做檢測。」楊明事後亦有接受傳媒訪問，指自己之前已經報警，更稱受害者不止他一個人，例如姚瑩瑩、曹永廉等，所以警方都有立案調查。"},{"pid":"f603492cc0f53b1c0e555ce98879c0b3949e2dba","tid":2189002,"uid":321977,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T14:53:15.000Z","msg":"幫你登記咪去驗囉，做咩唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係撐政府咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648e32a673b763f0ae0087848e7afc580b0e8aff","tid":2189002,"uid":16659,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T14:53:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zwakg7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZwakg7d.jpg&h=8acdf24a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n楊明手足黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d9bfe5fafb8d0d9a0fc3ae64c7c629b7926140","tid":2189002,"uid":16659,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T14:54:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nOSZBGg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnOSZBGg.jpg&h=a3633742&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n怪錯左手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f424f3ee51e14b4f3e0e37c07730a4a4f9c705d0","tid":2189002,"uid":256952,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T14:56:24.000Z","msg":"耐人尋味"},{"pid":"026469bf027fb25419b00a9df17118d235fd3cac","tid":2189002,"uid":212168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"